title: BIG FACTS feat. BIRDMAN

description:
BIG FACTS delivers another classic conversation with one the cultural icons of our time, BIRDMAN. He speaks on Cash Money Records history, rumors and misconceptions, VERZUZ, not receiving his proper credit, his past issues with Charlamagne, his favorite ATL artist, signing DJ Swamp Izzo and more.
